[CONNECTION ESTABLISHED]

“KEEP AWAY!”

“What? I'm just here to-”

“You are nothing but a government agent! Get away from us!”

“So you have a problem with the new government?”

“A… problem? Your mind tricks won't work on us. You have no power over us! We burned all of the trees!”

“I see. Look, I mean you no harm. Let me he-”

“GET AWAY.”


[CONNECTION CLOSED]

I understand now. It seems the trees hitting the “homes of the regular people” was more than just an unlucky accident.
